\section*{Why This Matters for Philanthropy}
\vspace{-0.2em}

\begin{multicols}{2}
\subsection*{The Current Challenge}
\begin{itemize}[leftmargin=*,topsep=0pt,itemsep=0pt]
    \item Impact reports often contain valuable information buried in narrative form
    \item Donors struggle to compare impacts across different programs
    \item Beneficiaries lack voice in verification
    \item Manual audit processes are costly and time-consuming
\end{itemize}

\columnbreak

\subsection*{Our Solution}
Transform complex impact narratives into clear, verifiable statements that can be independently validated:
\begin{itemize}[leftmargin=*,topsep=0pt,itemsep=0pt]
    \item Convert narrative reports into specific, measurable claims
    \item Enable direct beneficiary verification
    \item Generate portable, reusable impact credentials
    \item Streamline third-party audits
\end{itemize}
\end{multicols}

